            <title>[HBASE-10973] CatalogTracker can share ZK connection with regionserver</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10973</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, CatalogTracker has its own ZK connection even when it is used in the server side. It could share one connection with the server.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
