                            <comment id="13968658" author="jxiang" created="Mon, 14 Apr 2014 18:48:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In server side, we do pass the shared zk object to the CatalogTracker. However, in the HConnection, it creates another zk object/connection. I was thinking that the HConnection in CatalogTracker should use the shared zk object too. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
